        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.70 - Faster Position Bar for Basic SCORM</h3>

            <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Fix slow position bar display for Basic SCORM: initial progress message was sent with totalSlides=0 because generic detection hadn't run yet</li>
                <li>Position bar now appears with the first progress message instead of waiting for the generic detection interval</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Changes</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Early total slides detection: try findGenericScormContent() + getGenericTotalSlides() inline before sending initial progress</li>
                <li>Eliminates ~1.3s delay (was waiting for 1500ms setTimeout + 800ms interval for generic detection)</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Versions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.69: Preserve SCORM score-based progress in activity progress API</li>
                <li>v2.0.68: Fix progress 0% on resume, score &gt;100%, false completion</li>
                <li>v2.0.66: Auto-grade Basic SCORM from furthest slide progress</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
